{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_07_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 私のプライドはズタズタよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……いい話なのは、確かなんだけど\nこの仕事、やっぱり私には合わないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……It’s a good offer‚ no doubt about it.\nBut this job just isn't for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロには私よりふさわしい子達がいるでしょう？\n彼女達に頼んだ方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are girls at Hoshimi Prods more suited for it than me‚ right?\nIt'd be better to ask them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "先方が莉央さんにぜひ頼みたいそうなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The client specifically wants you‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今までにない花嫁像を表現して顧客拡大に繋げたい\n莉央さんとなら、それが出来ると",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They want to expand their customer base by showcasing a new type of bride.\nThey believe that can be achieved with you‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "でもブライダルのテレビCMでしょ？\nウエディングドレスを着て、にっこり笑う感じよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's for a bridal TV commercial‚ right?\nI'd have to wear a wedding dress and smile sweetly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのを否定する訳じゃないけど……\n私のイメージだと、似合わないんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not against that kind of thing‚ but…\nIsn't that image a poor fit for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、クールでかっこいい花嫁を表現したいから\n莉央さんの凛とした雰囲気がぴったりなんだそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ they want to portray a cool and stylish bride.\nThey think your dignified aura is perfect for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "先方のプロデューサーは\n莉央さん以外に考えられない、と言っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The client’s producer said\nthey couldn’t think of anyone else but you‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方、随分熱心にこの仕事を勧めるわね\nいつもなら、本人の意向が一番です、って言うじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re really pushing this job hard‚ aren’t you?\nUsually‚ you’re all about respecting my wishes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.4955797791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "も、もちろん莉央さんの意向が一番ですよ！\n特に、その……他意はないです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-of course‚ Rio-san’s wishes are the most important!\nThere’s absolutely no ulterior motive!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり今日の{user}さん、何か変よ\n……あ、そろそろ時間だわ。ライブ会場に行かないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something's definitely off about you today‚ {user}-san.\n…Oh‚ it’s almost time. We need to get to the concert venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7666669209,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11100.00000000001,
          "startTime": 79.8666669209
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "この件だけど、あまり期待はしないでちょうだい\n自分が納得出来ない仕事は、したくないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About this job‚ don’t get your hopes up.\nI don’t want to do work that I’m not convinced about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4333381652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（出来れば、やってほしいんだけどな……）\n（莉央さんのためにも）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I really hope she’ll take it…）\n（For her own sake‚ too…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3266.6673025999985,
          "startTime": 88.6000006359
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3533.34274289999,
          "startTime": 88.8666760762
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3500006359
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3500006359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します。ライブ、大成功でしたね\nって、あれ、莉央さんだけ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me. The live was a huge success!\nHuh‚ Rio-san‚ you’re the only one here…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3145209887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.8000006359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "屈辱だわ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is humiliating!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8000006359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！？　ど、どうしました？\nライブ、凄く良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa!? W-what’s wrong?\nThe live was amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0322594215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.333331426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの出来じゃないわよ！\nさっき、こころにこのネットニュースを見せられたの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not about the live!\nKokoro just showed me this online news article!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、その記事は……\n『お嫁さんにしたいアイドルランキング』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that article…\n‘Idols You’d Want as Your Bride Ranking’…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5279345066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.7999980927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "一位は遙子\n理由。家庭的な感じ。優しそう。癒される……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first place is Haruko.\nReasons: Domestic feel. Seems kind. Soothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1390428432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "これは分かるわ。イメージにぴったりだし\n私だって彼女に投票するわよ。だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get it. Fits her image perfectly.\nI would vote for her too. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.9666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.733331426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "私はランキング圏内ギリギリの三十位……\nしかも理由は、もの凄く気が強そうだけど料理上手",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm barely in the rankings at 30th place…\nAnd the reason? Seems very strong-willed but good at cooking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.233331426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "自分にも厳しいけど、夫にはもっと厳しそう\n規則正しく生きられそうだけど、家庭には笑顔もほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Strict with herself but even stricter with her husband.\nWould live a disciplined life‚ but home needs smiles too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……どのコメントも、一言余計なのよ！！\n私に投票しておいて、なんなの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Every comment has that one extra jab!!\nWhat’s with voting for me and then saying that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.3666647594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ、ランキングには入ったんですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ at least you made it into the rankings…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.3666647594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.9666627248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "でも最下位だったのよ！\nLizNoirの中で！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I was last place!\nIn LizNoir!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.6666627248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "愛は、見たことないくらい汗をかきながら\n必死にフォローしてくるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ sweating more than I’ve ever seen‚\ndesperately tried to console me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "葵には「花嫁がダメなら花婿になればいい」って\n言われたわ。……私、ひょっとして慰められたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi said‚ \"If you can't be a bride‚ be a groom instead.\"\nWas I… being comforted?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.6333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.4666627248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
