      "text": "こころには「あれ～？　莉央さんセンターなのに\nこころより下なんですねぇ～？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro teased me‚ \"Oh? Rio-san‚ you're lower than me\ndespite being the center?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.9999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.7195270323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
