      "text": "「もしかして、初めての敗北味わっちゃいました？」\nって煽られるし……私のプライドはズタズタよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Did you taste your first defeat?\"\nShe taunted… My pride is in shambles!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.7195270323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.1666627248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
