      "text": "あげくに、みんな私のこと腫れ物扱いして\n荷物をまとめてそそくさと帰って行ったのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then everyone treated me like I was fragile\nand quickly packed up and left!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.8333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "り、莉央さん、落ち着いて下さい！\nこんなのは一部のファンの遊びみたいなもので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rio-san‚ please calm down!\nThis is just a playful ranking by some fans…",
        "id": ""
