      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_07_01-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "昼間、やけに貴方がブライダルの仕事を勧めてきたのは\nこの結果を知っていたからじゃないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were pushing that bridal job so much today\nbecause you knew about this ranking?",
